{
  "conceptual": "\n<p sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"3\">The <strong sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"3\">Bistro Sample</strong> is a scene that demonstrates the use of a large number of assets, especially textures.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"5\"><img src=\"~/pages/samples/media/bistro-sample.jpg\" sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"5\" alt=\"Bistro Sample\"></p>\n<p sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"7\">The sample is based on the well-known <a href=\"https://developer.nvidia.com/orca/amazon-lumberyard-bistro\" sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"7\">Amazon Lumberyard Bistro</a> scene, adapted for ezEngine.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"9\">The sample can be downloaded directly from the ezEditor <a href=\"~/pages/docs/editor/dashboard.md\" sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"9\">dashboard</a>. Because of the amount of texture data, the download and unpacking may take a while. Once cloning is complete, any compressed archives in the project are extracted automatically.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"11\">For more details, see its <a href=\"https://github.com/jankrassnigg/ez-sample-bistro\" sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"11\">GitHub repository</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"see-also\" sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"13\">See Also</h2>\n<ul sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"15\">\n<li sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"15\"><a href=\"~/pages/samples/samples-overview.md\" sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"15\">Samples</a></li>\n<li sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"16\"><a href=\"~/pages/samples/store-sample.md\" sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"16\">Store Sample</a></li>\n<li sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"17\"><a href=\"~/pages/docs/editor/dashboard.md\" sourcefile=\"pages/samples/bistro-sample.md\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"17\">Dashboard</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
